name: Veeda Oncology
overview:
Veeda OncologyÂ® is a global oncology company and a member of the Veeda CR family of companies. While Veeda Oncology is a growing company, our management team has over 20 years of clinical experience in the oncology field with facilities located in the US, Europe and India. These strategic locations provide a tremendous feet-on-the-ground perspective to best serve our sponsors.

There expertise has evolved from strong working relationships with pharmaceutical, as well as biotech, companies. Previous clients range from very large established companies to start-up biotechnology companies. There mission is to provide outstanding oncology expertise that our clients require and expect to facilitate successful Phase I to Phase IV global programs.
